25:47.013 --> 25:48.748
Well, everyone except for you.

25:48.781 --> 25:50.950
It doesn't change anything.

25:50.983 --> 25:53.586
It's over.
We both know it.

25:53.620 --> 25:54.721
But Mom...
No, no. No.

25:54.754 --> 25:55.955
No lectures.

25:55.988 --> 25:57.590
This is not
a lecture.

25:57.624 --> 26:00.292
Dad is holding out hope.

26:00.326 --> 26:02.294
He thinks you might
change your mind.

26:02.328 --> 26:03.730
About kids.

26:03.763 --> 26:04.864
He does?

26:07.266 --> 26:08.901
I won't.

26:08.935 --> 26:10.169
I know.

26:10.202 --> 26:12.204
Wow.

26:15.174 --> 26:18.077
I-I really thought
we were in sync.

26:26.018 --> 26:27.987
RAFAEL:
They're gonna be great.

26:28.020 --> 26:29.922
PETRA:
Yes, they are.

26:31.958 --> 26:33.359
What's wrong?

26:33.392 --> 26:35.227
If me and my daughters

26:35.261 --> 26:36.996
are going to be
second-class citizens,

26:37.029 --> 26:39.331
you need to tell me
so I can be prepared.

26:39.365 --> 26:40.332
Second-class?

26:40.366 --> 26:42.234
To Jane and Mateo.

26:42.268 --> 26:43.770
You won't.

26:43.803 --> 26:45.237
We are now.

26:45.271 --> 26:48.107
And look, I know

26:48.140 --> 26:50.076
you didn't choose
this pregnancy.

26:50.109 --> 26:51.343
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 That's an understatement.

26:51.377 --> 26:54.313
But you did agree to be there.

26:54.346 --> 26:56.916
And if that's changed,
I need to know.

26:56.949 --> 26:58.317
No.

26:58.350 --> 27:00.853
I will be there.

27:00.887 --> 27:03.956
And I'm sorry
for making you feel that way.

27:09.028 --> 27:11.263
Okay, what is going on?
With the synchronized
swimmers?

27:11.297 --> 27:12.799
They're filming
a commercial.

27:12.832 --> 27:14.667
No, with Vests.
He just fired me.

27:14.701 --> 27:16.669
What?
What?
Luisa asked me to replace

27:16.703 --> 27:18.337
some bottles and he saw me
putting them back and now

27:18.370 --> 27:20.239
he thinks I stole them.
Don't worry.

27:20.272 --> 27:22.675
I'm calling her and
we are fixing this right now.

27:22.709 --> 27:26.045
Hola, Jane. Como esta?

27:26.078 --> 27:28.247
Luisa? Where are you?

27:28.280 --> 27:30.416
Just hanging out.
What about you?

27:30.449 --> 27:32.118
She's drunk.

27:32.151 --> 27:33.452
I am not!
Are you okay?

27:33.485 --> 27:35.287
Tell me where you are,
I'll come get you.

27:35.321 --> 27:37.323
(pop song playing
over phone)

27:39.258 --> 27:41.828
(same pop song playing,
louder and clearer)

27:41.861 --> 27:43.262
She's in the lounge.

27:43.295 --> 27:45.297
*

27:51.070 --> 27:52.371
(sighs, then gasps)

27:54.440 --> 27:57.076
Stay cool.

27:57.109 --> 27:58.978
I'm gonna count to three,

27:59.011 --> 28:01.147
then you guys are
gonna stand up.

28:01.180 --> 28:03.883
I'm gonna slip away.
(whooshes)

28:03.916 --> 28:07.353
One, two, three.

28:13.325 --> 28:16.162
I only had one drink.

28:16.195 --> 28:19.065
And five shots.

28:19.098 --> 28:21.100
And two shots.

28:21.133 --> 28:22.935
I'm sorry.

28:22.969 --> 28:24.470
Please don't take me
back to the Marbella.

28:24.503 --> 28:27.173
Luisa, you're in the Marbella.

28:27.206 --> 28:28.975
(gasps)

28:29.008 --> 28:30.309
I'm sorry.

28:30.342 --> 28:32.244
Sorry.

28:32.278 --> 28:35.114
I didn't mean to slip.

28:35.147 --> 28:36.415
(sighs)
Did you tell my brother?

28:36.448 --> 28:37.784
No. Did you?

28:37.817 --> 28:39.118
Yeah.
Luisa.

28:39.151 --> 28:41.187
Mm? Okay, no.

28:41.220 --> 28:43.189
Just, I didn't tell him

28:43.222 --> 28:46.725
because he's gonna be
so disappointed in me.

28:48.795 --> 28:51.730
I know, but still,
you have to tell him.

28:53.032 --> 28:54.733
Can I call my sponsor first?

28:56.202 --> 28:57.436
(exhales)

28:57.469 --> 28:59.471
Ay... Mm.

29:02.441 --> 29:04.110
Are you Luisa's sponsor?

29:04.143 --> 29:07.113
No.

29:08.547 --> 29:11.250
Oh... But look,
I'll take care of her.

29:11.283 --> 29:14.887
When she wakes up, she should
probably talk to her brother.

29:14.921 --> 29:17.389
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 And speaking of big
 scary talks...

29:17.423 --> 29:19.291
We can't do this anymore--

29:19.325 --> 29:23.195
act like we didn't
break up, because...

29:23.229 --> 29:25.497
we're really just putting
off the inevitable.

29:25.531 --> 29:29.401
I'm not gonna change my mind
about having kids.

29:29.435 --> 29:31.103
Jane told you?

29:31.137 --> 29:32.571
Yeah, she did.

29:32.604 --> 29:35.407
But it was good,
it-it helped me see.

29:35.441 --> 29:39.145
We're not gonna feel broken up
unless we take a step back.

29:39.178 --> 29:40.913
Not see each other as much.

29:40.947 --> 29:43.049
So...

29:43.082 --> 29:46.085
maybe take Jane
to the Tiago premiere?

29:49.588 --> 29:51.790
(text alert whooshes)

29:57.596 --> 29:58.797
(laughs)

30:22.054 --> 30:23.522
Uh... uh...

30:23.555 --> 30:24.623
(phone rings)

30:24.656 --> 30:26.125
Michael,

30:26.158 --> 30:27.493
you can't.

30:27.526 --> 30:28.861
You're more important.

30:28.895 --> 30:30.863
I'm not losing you again, Jane.

30:30.897 --> 30:33.132
I told you the other night
that I would do

30:33.165 --> 30:34.500
anything to make this work,

30:34.533 --> 30:36.335
and if that's losing my job

30:36.368 --> 30:38.437
versus losing you, then...

30:38.470 --> 30:39.571
you win out,

30:39.605 --> 30:42.074
every single time.

30:49.481 --> 30:51.283
JANE: He loves his job.
How can I let him quit?

30:51.317 --> 30:53.219
It's not really
your choice, right?

30:53.252 --> 30:56.455
I mean, if he loves you
enough to...

30:56.488 --> 30:59.058
to sacrifice
something like that,

30:59.091 --> 31:01.093
i-it's up to him.

31:04.997 --> 31:06.999
Mom?

31:08.600 --> 31:10.402
(gasping):
Oh,

31:10.436 --> 31:11.370
my...

31:11.403 --> 31:14.373
Hon, you look beautiful.

31:14.406 --> 31:17.376
I'm glad you're going
to the premiere with your dad.

31:17.409 --> 31:18.410
But are you okay?

31:18.444 --> 31:20.679
Yes, I'm
totally fine.

31:20.712 --> 31:22.681
I'm gonna
order Chinese,

31:22.714 --> 31:24.483
fire up the DVR...

31:24.516 --> 31:27.419
I'm looking forward
to just relaxing.

31:27.453 --> 31:28.955
Go on.

31:30.622 --> 31:34.560
No, no, I don't want the
gluten-free, MSG-free egg rolls.

31:34.593 --> 31:37.129
I know that's my normal order.

31:37.163 --> 31:39.431
Just the regular
egg rolls tonight.

31:39.465 --> 31:41.467
For one.

31:52.278 --> 31:54.413
This British telenovela
is not that original.

31:54.446 --> 31:56.382
We did the Egyptian
deflowering the virgin

31:56.415 --> 31:58.650
then dying in her bed
on Amor de Arabia.

31:58.684 --> 32:00.419
Stop talking
and pay attention.

32:00.452 --> 32:01.954
This part's important.

32:01.988 --> 32:05.124
What?!
I assume?

32:05.157 --> 32:07.493
You watched this
without me?!
I'm sorry.

32:07.526 --> 32:09.428
I'm sorry.
No, no.

32:09.461 --> 32:11.563
That is, like, a fundamental
relationship rule.

32:11.597 --> 32:14.266
You wait before moving
forward on your DVR.

32:14.300 --> 32:17.536
(both laughing)

32:22.108 --> 32:23.442
(sighing)

32:23.475 --> 32:24.476
Forgot my phone.

32:28.714 --> 32:31.283
Mom? Are you okay?

32:31.317 --> 32:34.553
Sorry. Yeah.

32:34.586 --> 32:36.022
(gasps)

32:36.055 --> 32:37.689
I just don't know whether or not

32:37.723 --> 32:40.226
to start episode eight, because

32:40.259 --> 32:42.528
we were watching it
together, you know, and...

32:42.561 --> 32:44.430
Oh.

32:44.463 --> 32:46.565
Oh.

32:46.598 --> 32:49.268
(crying): And don't want to
move ahead without him.

32:50.602 --> 32:51.503
But I want to know
what happened

32:51.537 --> 32:53.305
to Lady Sybil, you know?

32:53.339 --> 32:54.773
Yeah, I know, Mom.

32:54.806 --> 32:58.477
(crying)
I know.

32:58.510 --> 33:01.080
Jane should be arriving
any minute.
No problem.

33:01.113 --> 33:04.583
We're a little
ahead of schedule.

33:04.616 --> 33:09.288
But listen, I've been thinking
about your stalker situation.

33:09.321 --> 33:10.489
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 I'll remind you,

33:10.522 --> 33:12.158
this is his stalker situation.

33:13.525 --> 33:16.295
And I'm concerned.

33:16.328 --> 33:18.397
Stalkers can be
really dangerous.

33:19.531 --> 33:21.333
I've set up
security on set,

33:21.367 --> 33:23.402
but what's your
situation like at home?

33:23.435 --> 33:25.204
Do you have a dead bolt?

33:25.237 --> 33:27.439
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 No, don't tell her, Rogelio.

33:27.473 --> 33:29.441
No. I lost the key.

33:29.475 --> 33:31.343
Weapons?

33:31.377 --> 33:33.545
Just the mace I keep
in my underwear drawer.

33:33.579 --> 33:34.780
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 This is torture!

33:34.813 --> 33:37.149
Okay, how about

33:37.183 --> 33:39.418
a password-protected
security system?

33:39.451 --> 33:41.353
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 I'm shaking tables over here.

33:41.387 --> 33:43.322
Password's the same
as every other password.

33:43.355 --> 33:46.358
Rogelio, or, "Rogelio1"
if a number is needed.

33:48.227 --> 33:50.496
Hmm. Oh, it's Jane.

33:50.529 --> 33:52.064
Um...

34:05.544 --> 34:07.646
You okay?

34:09.447 --> 34:11.583
Yeah. Yes.

34:11.617 --> 34:14.719
Jane is running late.
Her mom was upset.

34:14.753 --> 34:17.589
Oh, God, are you always going
to be a second-class citizen?

34:17.623 --> 34:20.192
What?
I'm sorry.

34:20.226 --> 34:22.094
I shouldn't speak
out of turn.

34:22.128 --> 34:24.230
No, it's okay.

34:26.632 --> 34:28.167
This is a big night for you.

34:28.199 --> 34:30.636
That's all.

34:31.670 --> 34:34.572
I wish Jane
turned up for you.

34:34.606 --> 34:38.510
Anyway, you should
walk the carpet.
Yeah.

34:38.543 --> 34:42.414
(reporters clamoring,
cameras clicking)

34:51.523 --> 34:53.792
LUISA:
 I just feel so alone.

34:53.824 --> 34:56.795
My parents are dead...

34:56.828 --> 34:59.231
my brother hates me...

34:59.265 --> 35:01.700
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 The love of her life died
 in front of her.

35:01.733 --> 35:06.538
So when this little voice
tells me to drink,

35:06.572 --> 35:10.676
even just one,
to take the edge off...

35:10.709 --> 35:13.279
Well, I don't have
a little voice.

35:13.312 --> 35:16.548
I have a big voice.

35:16.582 --> 35:19.718
You need to go
back to rehab.

35:20.919 --> 35:23.455
So that when you're out,

35:23.489 --> 35:25.691
and you're better...

35:29.895 --> 35:33.332
...I can take you out.

35:33.365 --> 35:36.668
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 At last, a step forward.

35:38.670 --> 35:40.672
Which brings us here, now.

35:42.374 --> 35:43.609
Hey, Dad.

35:45.444 --> 35:46.612
I've been
looking for you.

35:46.645 --> 35:48.647
Why aren't you at
the after party?

35:48.680 --> 35:50.582
I just needed some air.

35:50.616 --> 35:52.918
Well, Tiago was great.

35:52.951 --> 35:55.421
I-I'm, I'm really sorry
that I missed the carpet.

35:55.454 --> 35:58.290
I understand your mother
was having a tough time.

35:58.324 --> 36:00.892
Exactly.
And she's more
important to you than me.

36:00.926 --> 36:02.761
Wait. Wait. What?!

36:02.794 --> 36:04.630
Well, you chose her over me.

36:04.663 --> 36:07.199
No, it was just because she
was upset about the breakup.

36:07.233 --> 36:09.901
So was I, and tonight
was a huge night

36:09.935 --> 36:11.770
for me, and you didn't show up.

36:11.803 --> 36:14.973
So the only Tiago related
hashtag trending

36:15.006 --> 36:17.409
was hashtag Rolonelio.

36:17.443 --> 36:19.678
You made a choice.

36:19.711 --> 36:22.348
At least own it.

36:22.381 --> 36:25.984
I'm really sorry, Dad.

36:26.017 --> 36:29.955
I just think
I need some space right now.

36:31.723 --> 36:33.892
Uh...

36:42.768 --> 36:43.735
I just feel so badly.

36:43.769 --> 36:45.371
I know.

36:45.404 --> 36:47.573
I'm sorry
I put you in that position.

36:47.606 --> 36:49.775
I e-mailed him a long apology,
lots of emojis. I won't be long.

36:49.808 --> 36:51.410
Where are you now?

36:51.443 --> 36:53.011
Taking Dad's advice, actually.

36:53.044 --> 36:55.747
I'm owning my choice.

36:57.316 --> 36:59.718
Michael is willing
to give up his job.

36:59.751 --> 37:02.321
Does that make it okay?

37:02.354 --> 37:04.823
I didn't think so,

37:04.856 --> 37:06.692
because it's not about that.

37:06.725 --> 37:08.827
The problem is
I'm choosing him.

37:08.860 --> 37:10.496
And I am

37:10.529 --> 37:11.930
choosing him.

37:11.963 --> 37:14.700
Either accept it, or don't,
but if you don't,

37:14.733 --> 37:17.803
you're the one who is making it
worse on our son,

37:17.836 --> 37:19.538
not me.

37:20.772 --> 37:22.974
I don't want to be replaced.

37:23.008 --> 37:26.945
What?! No, you won't be.

37:26.978 --> 37:30.416
Hey, you won't be.

37:30.449 --> 37:31.850
You're Mateo's dad.

37:33.852 --> 37:35.854
Yeah.

37:35.887 --> 37:38.857
I'll try.

37:38.890 --> 37:41.259
Thank you.

37:56.908 --> 37:58.444
(elevator bell dings)

37:58.477 --> 37:59.845
(elevator door closes)

38:05.551 --> 38:07.052
What are you doing here?
You asked

38:07.085 --> 38:11.056
what to expect from me when the
babies come, so, here it goes.

38:11.089 --> 38:12.358
I will be there...

38:12.391 --> 38:14.059
for all of it.

38:14.092 --> 38:15.494
I'll be the night nurse,

38:15.527 --> 38:16.862
I'll wake up with them
every three hours.

38:16.895 --> 38:18.497
I will feed them,
I will burp them.

38:18.530 --> 38:20.766
What?
It's everything
that I wanted to do

38:20.799 --> 38:22.100
with Mateo and Jane,
but I never got the chance.

38:22.133 --> 38:23.769
I'll even put in a door
between our suites,

38:23.802 --> 38:27.373
so that I can go
back and forth.
Rafael, stop.

38:27.406 --> 38:28.807
What's going on?

38:28.840 --> 38:31.009
I want to be there...

38:31.042 --> 38:33.612
with the babies,

38:33.645 --> 38:35.614
with you.

38:35.647 --> 38:38.884
You are not a second-class
citizen, Petra, and...

38:42.421 --> 38:44.890
Maybe I made a mistake.

38:47.993 --> 38:50.896
What happened?

38:50.929 --> 38:53.098
Excuse me?
I'm guessing

38:53.131 --> 38:57.035
Jane rejected you in some way,
so now you're here?

38:58.704 --> 39:00.906
I'm not
a second-class citizen, Raf.

39:02.508 --> 39:04.910
But I'm not
a second choice, either.

39:06.044 --> 39:07.813
You should go.

39:11.783 --> 39:14.920
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 Which brings us here.

39:14.953 --> 39:17.656
Hey.
Hey.

39:17.689 --> 39:20.392
Are you alone?
Yup.

39:20.426 --> 39:24.830
But I'm not planning
on going home alone.

39:24.863 --> 39:27.933
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 And neither, for the record,
 was Jane.

39:27.966 --> 39:30.669
WOMAN:
One, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight.

39:30.702 --> 39:33.739
One, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight.

39:33.772 --> 39:35.774
One, two, three,
four, five...

39:35.807 --> 39:37.743
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 And that's when she saw him.

39:37.776 --> 39:40.078
WOMAN:
...three, four, five,
six, seven, eight.

39:40.111 --> 39:42.681
One, two, three, four,
five, six, seven...

39:42.714 --> 39:45.717
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 And he saw her.

39:50.088 --> 39:52.958
(bright Broadway-style
melody playing)

40:22.521 --> 40:24.956
*

40:30.729 --> 40:31.997
WOMAN:
 Guys, we're trying to rehearse.

40:32.030 --> 40:34.432
Can you make out
somewhere else?

40:36.602 --> 40:39.104
(both snickering quietly)

40:39.137 --> 40:42.207
(bright, Broadway-style
melody resumes)

40:42.240 --> 40:44.843
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 Aw. And I hate
 to burst this bubble.

40:51.917 --> 40:53.685
Paola!

40:53.719 --> 40:55.487
Thank God it's you.

40:55.521 --> 40:57.589
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 But that is what I'm here for.

40:57.623 --> 41:00.225
I thought it was a crazy person
sitting there in the dark.

41:00.258 --> 41:01.860
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 You thought right!

41:01.893 --> 41:03.662
No problem.
And so you know,

41:03.695 --> 41:06.031
I've taken care of all the
security measures we discussed.

41:06.064 --> 41:08.934
I had new locks installed.

41:10.068 --> 41:11.970
I also had

41:12.003 --> 41:14.105
a new security system put in.

41:14.139 --> 41:15.974
(beeping)

41:16.007 --> 41:17.909
And I installed

41:17.943 --> 41:22.080
bars in all the windows
so no one can ever get out.

41:22.113 --> 41:25.617
You mean,
so no one could ever get in?

41:25.651 --> 41:26.918
No.

41:26.952 --> 41:28.787
That's not

41:28.820 --> 41:31.089
what I mean.

41:31.122 --> 41:33.792
Rogo.

41:33.825 --> 41:36.762
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 And it should be noted,
 that's when he realized...

41:36.795 --> 41:39.598
There's only one person in
the world who has ever called me

41:39.631 --> 41:41.967
by that name,
my old prison pen pal Lola.

41:42.000 --> 41:43.702
So you remember me?

41:43.735 --> 41:44.970
But you-you couldn't be.

41:45.003 --> 41:47.939
She was in jail when
you worked for J. Lo.

41:47.973 --> 41:49.875
LATIN LOVER NARRATOR:
 And that's when he heard

41:49.908 --> 41:51.843
the scariest words of all.

41:51.877 --> 41:54.680
I've never met J. Lo.

